debug: SELECT DISTINCT c.*, p.nome as paciente_nome, p.telefone, (SELECT TRIM(GROUP_CONCAT(" ", t2.descricao)) FROM `transacao` t2 WHERE t2.id_servico > 0 AND t2.tipo = 0 AND t2.id_comanda = c.id) AS servicos FROM `comanda` c INNER JOIN `transacao` t ON t.id_comanda = c.id LEFT JOIN `#__paciente` p ON p.id = c.id_paciente  WHERE c.status LIKE '%'  AND (t.data between '2020-01-01' AND '2023-08-31') ORDER BY c.status ASC, c.id DESC
